title: Pamphlet Supplement
title-note: US compiled statutes and/or US code
aka: United States Code Annotated: Pamphlet Supplement
additional-note: The exact title varied somewhat by issue.  Issues of this serial were typically renewed as books, and not as periodicals. Some issues covered the Statues and Code separately, some together. Some cumulative supplements after this date also have active renewals. Pamphlet numbering may have reset periodically.
